primary.context: Customer has never logged in before and needs to set up their owner's account.
primary.detail: Agent verified the customer and sent a Clubhouse registration link to their updated email address.

steps: Customer requested help logging into their account.
Agent performed account lookup and verification using name, phone, and state.
Customer clarified they need to set up a new account.
Agent identified outdated contact information and updated the email and phone for the session.
Agent sent the Clubhouse registration link and confirmed completion.

clarifications.note: Agent confirmed if registration link was needed.

corrections.note: Customer corrected outdated email and phone digit.

actions.detail: Verified name and state of residence.

insights.summary: The customer needed to set up their owner's account for the first time. The AI successfully verified the caller, updated their contact information, and sent the Clubhouse registration link.
